{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_01","textHome":"当知晓了一切之后，我作为魔法少女的骄傲，@就脆弱地崩溃了……那时，我的内心被@恐怖和绝望充斥。但是现在不一样了。@我为了全新的理念而战斗。我会拯救你的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_18","textHome":"高价的茶具配上红茶和蛋糕。@今天就一起欢迎最棒的终结吧。@对我们来说，毫无痛苦的终结就要开始了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_19","textHome":"神圣的力量，在我的体内流淌……"}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_20","textHome":"为了新的目标……我不会停下脚步……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_21","textHome":"我曾经宣扬的正义太过于渺小。@在我认识到这一点的时候，深深地被震撼了，@但也因此有了现在的我。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_22","textHome":"如果这个世界一定要有恶存在的话，@那可能就是现在的我了。为了把灾祸@转变为幸福，我所做的事情，也可以称之为正义。@是的，我现在就是这么坚信的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":9.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_23","textHome":"为了那些仰慕我的人们，我绝不能屈服。@但是，我也一定要冲破围绕在我们魔法少女@周围的真相。因为这就是我重生的意义。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_24","textHome":"欢迎~我正喝着茶在思考圣诞礼物该送什么。@有什么好主意吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_25","textHome":"早上也已经变得很冷了，没有感冒吧？@期待欢乐的圣诞节之余也要保重身体哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_26","textHome":"差不多该到午饭时间了。@寒冷的季节果然会想吃热乎的东西呢。@晚上的话……做炖肉吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_27","textHome":"能陪我去买点东西吗？@我想去买点圣诞树的装饰品。@今年想稍微弄得漂亮一点。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_03","textHome":"魔女……@为了解放魔法少女必须要拿到悲叹之种……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_28","textHome":"晚上果然很冷呢～啊，要喝热巧克力吗？冬天除了红茶以外，我也经常喝热巧克力。@会暖和起来哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_29","textHome":"你不觉得下雪的景色很神秘吗？@雪花悄无声息地就飘落，堆积起来。@今年若是一个白色圣诞节就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_30","textHome":"我们也要好好履行作为魔法少女的职责才行。@如果不做个好孩子，圣诞老人是不会来的。@呵呵，开个玩笑。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_31","textHome":"不知道今天能走到哪一步。@重要的是要牢牢地守住自我，不被迷惑。@来，我们走吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_32","textHome":"没事的哟！@只要有我们的阵容在，就没有什么好担心的。@至少我是这么认为的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_33","textHome":"每年到了这个时候，@我都会去喜欢的点心店预约圣诞树枝蛋糕。@放心吧，今年的我已经预约好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_34","textHome":"呵呵……这身衣服看上去真可爱，我很喜欢。@虽说平常的魔法少女服我也喜欢，@但这样特别的装扮我也并不讨厌哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_35","textHome":"一年中我最喜欢的活动就是圣诞节了。@仅仅是看到街道上绚丽的彩灯，@就不禁心跳加速。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_36","textHome":"虽然现在非常冷，但是我还是喜欢@在冬天的夜晚到阳台上看星星。@你看，因为夜空很明净所以看起来很漂亮吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_37","textHome":"果然在这样的季节里会想听圣诞歌呢。@惯例的圣诞歌结束后，还有喜欢的CD能放。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_04","textHome":"帮助同志是理所当然的，@只不过一直被叫去帮忙就有些难了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_38","textHome":"失去家人，成为名为魔法少女的神秘存在后，@未曾想过还能像这样迎来热闹的圣诞节。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_39","textHome":"真是不可思议，@明明已经过了相信圣诞老人的年纪……@为何还是会在平安夜里心怀期待呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_40","textHome":"袜子准备好了吗?……呵呵，开玩笑的。@圣诞快乐！可以收下我准备的礼物吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_41","textHome":"在海外，圣诞节总给人一种全家团圆的印象。@等我几时拥有了自己的家庭……@这样安稳的圣诞节感觉也不错呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_42","textHome":"那么，就由我来引领你吧。"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_43","textHome":"稍微幸福一点了吗？"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_44","textHome":"这就是我展示的道路。"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_45","textHome":"我不会让任何人绝望的。"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_46","textHome":"愿望就是不可侵犯的圣域。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_63","textHome":"我们的希望不容许被夺去。"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_05","textHome":"那些少女们能接受……这个事实吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":300}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_64","textHome":"就让你做个好梦吧。"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_65","textHome":"最终射击・圣夜！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_66","textHome":"这是奇迹的礼炮。"}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_02","textHome":"我是巴麻美。@当你辛苦得快要撑不住的时候就呼唤我，@我一定会来拯救你的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":101}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_13","textHome":"为了不忘记这个感觉，@就需要一步步地变强才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_14","textHome":"就算变强了也没办法安心……@最根本的问题还需要得到解决才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_15","textHome":"你还是不知道比较好哦。不该强行打听的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_16","textHome":"在战斗之前最重要的就是平心静气。@现在我需要的是一杯能让我做好觉悟的红茶。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":250000}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":250000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2500_00_17","textHome":"最近，我比以前更加珍惜喝红茶的时间了。@像这样能歇一口气的时间，真是无可替代。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":250000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":250000}]}]},"version":3}